00444 /*
00445  * The difference between single and multi-layer server affects only
00446  * nc_init() and nc_close() calls. Generally, single-layer application
00447  * can be executed and finish several times, even during a single
00448  * NETCONF session. A multi-layer application is expected to call
00449  * nc_close() only after it actually finished all its work and no
00450  * client is connected.
00451  */

00453 #define NC_INIT_SINGLELAYER 0x00002000 
00454 #define NC_INIT_CLIENT 0x00004000
